      </div>

      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 space-y-8">
        <h4 class="text-[10px] font-black text-[#030A8C] uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Resources</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-bold text-[#0D0D0D] text-sm">
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-[#F29F05]">KRA Guide 2026</a></li>
